Description:
------------

This demo illustrates the machanism for invoking the Java environment (Graphics, etc.)
from the UAL C++ applications

The source code is located in the ./src directory.

Requirements
------------

1. Java environment variables

setenv JAVA_HOME <home of Java distribution>
set path = ($JAVA_HOME/bin $path)
setenv LD_LIBRARY_PATH $JAVA_HOME/jre/lib/i386:$JAVA_HOME/jre/lib/i386/client:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH

2. Additional UAL environment variable

setenv UAL_JAVA

Usage:
------

make
cd linux
./demo



